	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can save money on buying food by keeping all the meat you get from the animals then going to a bakery and buy bread.&nbsp;&nbsp;Combine 1 meat and 1 bread to make a sandwich.  The bread cost around 1.3 silver but you can sell the sandwiches for over 3 silver ( if you are successful in making them). This technique has help me save a lot of money. the best meat is mammoth meat. It will make 5 sandwiches.<br><br>JasonB<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
